1.18
log
@add -delete option which can simplify the common case of wanting to delete
lots of files without the arcane -exec or error prone xargs.
code from freebsd.
ok millert
@
text
@/*	$OpenBSD: find.h,v 1.17 2015/03/15 00:41:28 millert Exp $ */
/*-
